			(property "Description" "MCP73831/2 LIPO Charger\n\n• VDD: 3.75 - 6V\n• Temp -40 - 85°C\n• Programmable Charge Rate: 15-500mA\n\nNOTE: STAT is a tri-state logic output on the MCP73831 and an open-drain output on the MCP73832.\n\nSOT23-5 with 4.2V output and tri-state logic on STAT = MCP73831T-2ACI/OT"
